title: Cowboy Junkies 1994-06-24 @ Bathurst Theater - Toronto, ON
description:
So, the first show might be out there a bit, but it&#039;s from that stellar 1994 tour that produced the  200 More Miles CD, the band&#039;s first official release. 1994 is still probably my favorite year, even though the albums to come produced even better material. However they were a little rawer back then, and some of my favorite songs, like "Ring on the Sill," got lots of plays.

 

The recording I have is an audience, but still sounds quite good.
